# Testing Standards

- Use `@testing-library/react` with `user-event`.
- Use screen queries (`getByRole`, `findByText`) instead of test IDs.
- Mock external APIs using `msw`.
- Keep tests under 15 lines each.
- Use a custom `renderWithProviders` if context/state is needed.
- Group test utilities under `/test-utils/`
